snippet.title: FitXR - Workouts For Everyone
snippet.description:
Working out has looked the same for way too long. Waking up at 6am? Getting naked in public? Burpees on repeat? No way.

FitXR is the VR fitness studio that is changing the game in fitness and bringing back some much-needed fun to working out. 

Start working out your own way now! Find out more at https://fitxr.com

Download FitXR from the Oculus Store: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/2327205800645550
